<subSubSection lastPageId="4" lastPageNumber="365" pageId="3" pageNumber="364" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="3.[151,1437,152,251]" pageId="3" pageNumber="364">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,324,152,179]" pageId="3" pageNumber="364">Diagnosis:</emphasis>
This new species of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Robineau-Desvoidy" authorityYear="1830" box="[556,674,152,178]" class="Insecta" family="Sciomyzidae" genus="Pherbellia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="364" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[556,674,152,178]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="364">Pherbellia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is similar to 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Zetterstedt" baseAuthorityYear="1846" box="[817,953,152,178]" class="Insecta" family="Sciomyzidae" genus="Pherbellia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="364" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="annulipes">
<emphasis box="[817,953,152,178]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="364">P. annulipes</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
but differs in the color of the femora, black in 
<emphasis box="[181,325,188,214]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="364">
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Zetterstedt" baseAuthorityYear="1846" box="[181,321,188,214]" class="Insecta" family="Sciomyzidae" genus="Pherbellia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="364" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="annulipes">P. annulipes</taxonomicName>
,
</emphasis>
yellow in 
<taxonomicName box="[446,527,188,214]" class="Insecta" family="Sciomyzidae" genus="Pherbellia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="364" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="jalili">
<emphasis box="[446,527,188,214]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="364">P. jalili</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. Especially in the shape of the surstyli is characteristic: rounded in 
<emphasis box="[1292,1436,188,214]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="364">
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Zetterstedt" baseAuthorityYear="1846" box="[1292,1432,188,214]" class="Insecta" family="Sciomyzidae" genus="Pherbellia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="364" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="annulipes">P. annulipes</taxonomicName>
,
</emphasis>
blunt in 
<taxonomicName box="[245,325,224,250]" class="Insecta" family="Sciomyzidae" genus="Pherbellia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="364" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="jalili">
<emphasis box="[245,325,224,250]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="364">P. jalili</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="3.[151,750,1029,1055]" lastBlockId="4.[151,993,1056,1118]" lastPageId="4" lastPageNumber="365" pageId="3" pageNumber="364">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,221,1029,1054]" pageId="3" pageNumber="364">FIG 2.</emphasis>
Lateral view of a male 
